      "textContent": "Röda flaggorKritisk · Snabb bennedbrytningBennedbrytning oproportionerlig mot plackbörda — särskilt ung patient → Misstänk Grad C, systemsjukdom (HIV, leukemi), aggressiv parodontit.Kritisk · AbscessbildningAkut parodontal abscess → dränage omedelbart. Se scenario Parodontal Abscess.Varning · SystemsjukdomOkontrollerad diabetes (HbA1c >10%), immunosuppression, neutropeni → Koordinera med läkare. Antibiotika kan vara indicerat.Varning · Tandrörlighet grad 3Tand rörlig i vertikalled eller spontant",
      "outerHTML": "<section class=\"rounded-[22px] p-7 md:p-8 mb-4\" role=\"alert\" aria-label=\"Röda flaggor — klinisk varning\" style=\"background:var(--status-danger);color:#fff;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(193,18,31,0.28)\"><h2 class=\"font-body font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-5 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 9v4m0 4h.01M10.3 3.86 1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.7 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.4 0Z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg>Röda flaggor</h2><ul class=\"space-y-4\" role=\"list\"><li class=\"border-b border-white/20 pb-3 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><p class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-1\">Kritisk · <!-- -->Snabb bennedbrytning</p><p class=\"text-sm text-white/85 leading-relaxed\">Bennedbrytning oproportionerlig mot plackbörda — särskilt ung patient → Misstänk Grad C, systemsjukdom (HIV, leukemi), aggressiv parodontit.</p></li><li class=\"border-b border-white/20 pb-3 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><p class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-1\">Kritisk · <!-- -->Abscessbildning</p><p class=\"text-sm text-white/85 leading-relaxed\">Akut parodontal abscess → dränage omedelbart. Se scenario Parodontal Abscess.</p></li><li class=\"border-b border-white/20 pb-3 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><p class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-1\">Varning · <!-- -->Systemsjukdom</p><p class=\"text-sm text-white/85 leading-relaxed\">Okontrollerad diabetes (HbA1c &gt;10%), immunosuppression, neutropeni → Koordinera med läkare. Antibiotika kan vara indicerat.</p></li><li class=\"border-b border-white/20 pb-3 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><p class=\"font-bold text-sm mb-1\">Varning · <!-- -->Tandrörlighet grad 3</p><p class=\"text-sm text-white/85 leading-relaxed\">Tand rörlig i vertikalled eller spontant rörlig → Hopeless prognosis. Diskutera extraktion.</p></li></ul></section>",
